{"ts":"2026-05-31T20:15:19.768Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-g3xl"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Drift-lock the .agents/plugins/marketplace.json (pm-local) manifest in the plugin contract test"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"The repo has three marketplace manifests; the drift test reconciles only root marketplace.json and .claude-plugin/marketplace.json. The third, .agents/plugins/marketplace.json (name pm-local), has no test/code/docs reference and can silently rot (it currently lists only pm-codex and omits pm-claude, with no enforced version)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:ci","area:docs","governance","living-map","plugins","pm-cli"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-31T20:15:19.768Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-31T20:15:19.768Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"tests/integration/claude-plugin-contract.spec.ts (or scripts/smoke-claude-plugin.mjs) reads .agents/plugins/marketplace.json and asserts its plugin list and version stay consistent with plugins/*/.codex-plugin/plugin.json and plugins/*/.claude-plugin/plugin.json; CI fails if the manifest drifts."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-u9d0"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"fd9e71cf0acbcd3934d78b11653156b757d2fc1f279e67e14b5d3147a4d66046","message":""}
